===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{UK|colloquial|lang=en}} A [[fool]], a [[twit]].
#: ''Now you've broken it, you '''twerp'''!''
# {{US|colloquial|lang=en}} A small or [[puny]] person; one regarded as insignificant, contemptible.
#: ''Get out of my way, you little '''twerp'''!''
# {{US|colloquial|lang=en}} A person who can be [[bully|bullied]] playfully, or easily teased. Sometimes used as a pet-name (often for a younger sibling).

